channel.description: is it illegal to make a 614 Webclient? people are asking me to make one and i just dont wana go to jail. so can someone awnser this?

item.title: 614 question
item.dc:creator: @Andrew_Ferguson The317Guy
item.description:
@Andrew_Ferguson wrote:

Unless your getting 2000+ players on your server (which will never happen for any server) Jagex has no real right to shut you down. The server files (which we have since re-written our own way) and client files, were released by Jagex employee to the internet and unless your getting the said amount of players on your server you cause no real monetary gain issues to Jagex, thus they don’t give a shit.
